## Limitations
The report is limited by the availability of up-to-date academic research and the reliance on publicly available online resources, which may not always provide comprehensive scientific data. Additionally, the perspectives included are primarily from Western viewpoints, which may not represent global attitudes towards animal captivity. Further research could include more diverse cultural perspectives and empirical studies on the long-term effects of caging on different animal species.

